UINT16 ToneAudioDevice::StartParam::mix_factor
 

Kind of volume with range 0-0x7FFF.
0 - no sound, 0x7FFF is max.
0x4000 will result in a volume level equal to speech.

UINT16 ToneAudioDevice::StartParam::play_count
 

How often the tone is to be played.
